  "detailed_description": "In the puzzle game Puffer Pop, you leverage your environment to dodge sharks, eat crabs, and rearrange bubbles. To survive the sharks, you'll need to puff up and show your spikes. However, there is a catch—you need air bubbles to do that... and a bubble only inflates a single side...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418980/extras/f77060899b9f292d7263303503643b84.poster.avif?t=1702687173\" width=506 height=506 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418980/extras/f77060899b9f292d7263303503643b84.webm?t=1702687173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418980/extras/f77060899b9f292d7263303503643b84.mp4?t=1702687173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To reach the bubbles, you'll have to buy time by forcing enemies to run into and around each other. To take our your predators, you'll have to lure them into your spike-y sides. Sometimes, you may even need to rearrange the level to your advantage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418980/extras/1d90edb0453df20f6d86d4c9f1bb5f3d.poster.avif?t=1702687173\" width=506 height=506 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418980/extras/1d90edb0453df20f6d86d4c9f1bb5f3d.webm?t=1702687173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2418980/extras/1d90edb0453df20f6d86d4c9f1bb5f3d.mp4?t=1702687173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Relaxing turn-based gameplay with ocean ambiance<br></li><li>Small, self-contained levels for quick play sessions (once 